name: Prioritisation
description: Results of prioritisation of NORMAN substances using the NORMAN Prioritisation Framework

name: Substance Database
description: A merged list of NORMAN substances; Central Database to access various lists of substances for suspect screening and prioritisation

name: Suspect List Exchange
description: Central Database to access various lists of substances for suspect screening and prioritisation

name: Antibiotic Resistant Bacteria/Genes
description: A database of ARBs/ARGs in environmental matrices

name: Substance Factsheets
description: A summary information on individual substances from all NORMAN Database System modules

name: Bioassays Monitoring Data
description: A database of data obtained by analysis of environmental samples with bioassayss

name: Indoor Environment
description: A database of data in indoor environment matrices

name: Ecotoxicology
description: A platform for systematic collection and evaluation of ecotoxicity studies for harmonised derivation of environmental quality standards

name: Passive Sampling
description: A database of data obtained with passive samplers

name: Chemical Occurrence Data
description: A database of geo-referenced monitoring data on emerging substances

name: MassBank Europe
description: A database of mass spectra of emerging substances to support identification of unknown substances

name: Digital Sample Freezing Platform
description: A database of mass chromatograms obtained by LC-HR-MS for retrospective screening of environmental samples
